Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gostaria que tivessem algo menor.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.40,0:00:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Lorde Hak, o que está fazendo aqui no meio da noite?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.66,0:00:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe. Eu o acordei?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, não quis dizer isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.28,0:00:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A porta está quebrada.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Queria uma espada pequena e um arco.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Está indo caçar?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.46,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou indo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso ficar fora por um tempo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe incomodá-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lorde Hak, está pagando por estas coisas?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Você sempre manda colocar em sua conta.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por tudo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.60,0:00:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenha uma vida longa.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.27,0:00:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está tão sério agora,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.52,0:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,seu Demônio Relâmpago idiota.
