Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Que criatura mais adorável!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.61,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me acariciá-lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me segurá-lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hean-dea, fique vivo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito bem. Irei checar os comerciantes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Também irei enterrar este corpo enquanto isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas estou vivo, eu acho...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ande, ande.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rina!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Minha nossa. Acabou de me chamar de "madame"?
